    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Meetâ buht/ un ar linnu Johſtu buhs winnam apjohſtees/ un ar to linnu Zeppuri apſegtees/ fchahs irr tahsfwehtas Drehbes/ tapehz buhs winnam fatwu Meeſu ar Uhdeni pehrt/ kad wiꞥſch tehp apwilkts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Iſraëta Behrnu Draudſes buhs winnam diwi Ahſchus par Grehku-Uppuri nemt/ un weenn Aunu par Deꞥamu-Uppuri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz to buhs Aäronnam ta Grehku-Uppura Wehrſi/ kas preeſch winnu irr/ uppureht/ un preeſch few un fawa Namma Salihdsinaschann darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winnam buhs arridsan tohs diwi Abschus nemt/ un tohs ta KUNGA Preeſcha weſt/ preeſch tahs Sa-eefchanas Telts Durwim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Aäronnam buhs pahr teem diwiAbscheem Metlus mest/ weenn Mejlu preeſch ta KUNGA/ un weenn Metlu preeſch to palaischannu Ahſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs Aäronnam to Ahſi/ us ko tee Metli preeſch ta KUNGA krittufchi peerwest/ un to par Grehku-Uppuri fatafiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet to Ahſi/us ko tee Metli irr nahkufcht/ fa tas weens palaischans Ahſis effus/ buhs winnam dſihwu ta KUNGA Preeſcha weſt/ Salihdsinaschannu par winnam darriams/ fa to par weenu palaischannu Ahſi Tuefneſi warr palaist.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Aäronnam buhs ta Grehku-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Uppura Wehrſi/ kas preeſch ferr pascha irr peewest/ un preeſch few pascha/ un preeſch farriht/un ta Grehku-Uppura Wehrſi/ kas preeſch few pascha irr nokaut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winnam buhs arridsa weenu Wihraka-Trauku pillu a dedsamahin Ohglehim no ta Alta ra nemt preeſch ta KUNGA/ winnas Saujas pillas ar Kwehpya-Sahlehm no Jagrubſtahm jau kas Smarſchas Sahlehm/ un winnam buhs tahs ais t Preeſchweſkannu neſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnam buhs tah Kwehpya-Sahles us to Uggun lift preeſch ta KUNGA/ ka tah Kwehpinaſchanas Duhmi to Salihdsinaschanas-Wahku/kas us t Leezibu irr apklahj/ka tas ne mirſt\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnam buhs no ta Wehrſcha Affini nemt/ un ar fawu Pirkſtu us to Salihdsinaschanas-Wahku prett teem flazziht un preeſch to Salihdsinaschanas Wahku buhs winnam feptinkahrt ar fawn Pirkſtu no ta Affins flazziht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to buhs winnam ta Grehku-Uppura Ahſi/kas preeſch faudim irr nokaut/ un winnam Affini ais ta Preeſchweſkannu Eekſchu neſt/un tam buhs ar winnam Affini ta patt darriht/ itt ka winſch ar ta Wehrſcha Affini darrijs irr/ un to flazziht us to Salihdsinaschanas-Wahku/ un preeſch ta Salihdsinaschanas-Wahka.\n"
    }
  ],
